app_description: Lemon Diary is a portable App for recording handbooks and diaries. Use exquisite stickers at will to record your daily life. The design is simple and easy to use. Material Library Exquisite and lovely material library stickers backgrounds cute fonts and other materials to help you record your daily life Graphic Text pictures record daily life calendar Calendar browsing don t miss important days easy to view password protection Password function to protect privacy Font Selection Use multiple fonts at will Share Diary Share diary pictures with one click Quickly use Lemon Diaryn to record your life.
